00:22:44.50,00:22:46.59
Or let me put it another way.

00:22:46.67,00:22:49.59
Whose word are they going to accept?

00:22:49.67,00:22:52.13
I'll tell you what I'm willing to do.

00:22:52.22,00:22:55.30
So far, all I have written[br]in this report...

00:22:55.35,00:22:58.89
is that you and Lejeune were killed[br]while out on patrol.

00:22:58.97,00:23:01.14
I'll fix this to read[br]that you made your way back...

00:23:01.23,00:23:03.52
after becoming separated[br]during the skirmish.

00:23:03.60,00:23:06.27
- That'll end the matter.[br]- You killed Lejeune. You know that.

00:23:06.36,00:23:08.02
- It was an accident.[br]- You threw that grenade.

00:23:08.11,00:23:11.78
I'd give anything if it hadn't happened.[br]That's the truth.

00:23:11.86,00:23:15.65
