00:36:13.69,00:36:16.49
a good part of your men[br]never left their own trenches.

00:36:16.53,00:36:20.24
Colonel Dax, I'm going to have ten men[br]from each company in your regiment...

00:36:20.32,00:36:23.07
tried under penalty of death[br]for cowardice.

00:36:23.16,00:36:25.74
- Penalty of death?[br]- For cowardice!

00:36:25.83,00:36:28.04
They've skim milk in their veins[br]instead of blood.

